properties.Name: PumpServiceType
properties.Description:
The type of service associated with the pump.

Ex:
-  High pressure 
-  Common low pressure booster 
-  Low pressure booster to HPP 
-  2nd pass 
-  3rd stage 
-  3rd stage booster 
-  4th stage 
-  ERD booster
-  Seawater intake 
-  Ultrafiltration backwash 
-  Ultrafiltration feed
-  Low pressure booster
-  CIP

Columns.Name: PumpServiceTypeId
